      <title>中国对招商银行前行长判处死刑缓期执行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/china-hands-ex-merchants-bank-president-suspended-death-sentence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年，中国当局对招商银行前行长田惠宇提出贿赂和内幕交易指控，判处其死刑缓期执行。]]></description>
