      <title>尼日利亚央行撼动市场，美元交易量翻倍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/ngn-usd-nigeria-s-dollar-volumes-double-as-central-bank-shakes-up-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在尼日利亚央行宣布一系列措施，使奈拉能够更自由地兑美元交易后，尼日利亚外汇市场的美元交易量增加了一倍多。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/ngn-usd-nigeria-s-dollar-volumes-double-as-central-bank-shakes-up-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 09:01:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
